title: Dru Hill - DRU HILL 320cbr (Big Papi) 1996 R&B Music
description:
Source: 1996 CD
 

 
By BklynBabylon
[quote]I have been listening to this CD since the year it came out and I have never gotten tired of it. This is a REAL classic CD, one that every R&B fan should own. Tracks like "Love's Train", "In My Bed", "April Showers", "Tell Me", "Do You Believe?", "All Alone, "5 Steps", and "Never Make A Promise" are some of the best songs that I have ever heard by a male R&B group. They all show their range on every song which makes it so special. I wish they would come out with another classic!!! I miss DRU HILL!!!![/quote]
